    "causal_summary": "Plan the Deep Research mode's shadow-parity harness over the typed event-ledger substrate. The harness runs the ledger path beside the legacy emitter for init, iterative gather/analyze, convergence detection, synthesis, resume, and memory-save handoff; canonicalizes only declared transport volatility; diffs the mode projection event-for-event; and blocks authority cutover on any unexplained semantic difference. This is planning only and does not authorize a ledger cutover or remove the legacy writer.",
